Class FTCRManeuver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.ftcr.FTCRManeuver

  • public class FTCRManeuver
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents information about maneuver on the FTCRRoute.

    IMPORTANT: FTCRManeuver is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.
